{"tid":2184280,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 回鍋肉 + 蕃茄傻仔湯","createTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T12:51:13.000Z","uid":260581,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c8703851690a0590c391097a8dd8981c7177c5c2","tid":2184280,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚終於唔係食牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便清埋樽豆瓣醬 所以今晚整回鍋肉<br />\n我都係第一次整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先用火槍噴表皮 然後用鋼絲刷 清乾淨個面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFHfko5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFHfko5.jpg&h=b57a5e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗乾淨就 蔥薑 紹酒 花椒粒 <br />\n凍水落 水滾煲15-20分鐘<br />\n上網d人好似會煮到熟曬 不過我冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煮完就即刻沖水冷卻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4SxKYbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4SxKYbB.jpg&h=d8878c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凍左就可以切片備用<br />\n料頭有京蔥 蔥段 薑 蒜 辣椒 洋蔥 椰菜同豆豉<br />\n調味就豆瓣醬 海洋醬 黃豆醬同生抽 少少鹽同糖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFkXyLF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFkXyLF.jpg&h=fda0a7bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先爆左d豬腩先 爆到出曬油之後<br />\n就落豆瓣醬炒香<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBuNbGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBuNbGW.jpg&h=8e3bd875&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWYup1Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWYup1Y.jpg&h=fe9566a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就 除左椰菜同蔥綠 倒曬d配料落去炒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnJeA8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnJeA8Z.jpg&h=412c19f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後加椰菜 炒到淋身就可以<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RoiinT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RoiinT.jpg&h=97722e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩~~~~今晚呢個好好食架<br />\n真係冇呃你~~~ um等我試下先<br />\n嘩 真係無得頂 好正架~~~<br />\n喉嚨好c伏<br />\n一拎到出去就好快清曬<br />\n好食架 正啊~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PD5D2PK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPD5D2PK.jpg&h=8f3962c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Y0pdWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Y0pdWq.jpg&h=34b9b0b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"689be6ea644df98e6edda6cd4f3bf9172ea0d426","tid":2184280,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"1."},{"pid":"1c7ad7c060da61835929637c923b26813c8d5748","tid":2184280,"uid":209310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c77c278cb65e8203c787283fc9c84c6961f9711f","tid":2184280,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠辣?"},{"pid":"0a800cd6595f37265e86419a75479670daca2f7e","tid":2184280,"uid":209310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689be6ea644df98e6edda6cd4f3bf9172ea0d426","tid":2184280,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"1."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f75578b2df4dc09ba64bb31e8e094f8333c93e","tid":2184280,"uid":293632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class